<h3 id="keep-ones-mouth-shut">keep one’s mouth shut</h3>
<p>1.<strong>保守秘密；守口如瓶</strong>  </p>
<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>mouthful /'maʊθfʊl/ n [C]   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a mouthful of food
一口食物</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He eats each mouthful with great enjoyment.
